---
title: Gambas Pil Pil Inspired Double Prawns with Basmati Rice and Roasted Peppers
description: A world-famous tapas dish, 'pil pil' is a word used in Spanish and Basque cuisines that describes a sauce made with garlic and chilli-infused olive oil. Some say 'pil pil' is the sound of popping garlic as it cooks in the hot oil.
